Task Management
=======================

create <task_name>
  Creates a new task

delete <task_name>
  Deletes a task

use <task_name>
  Switches active task to the one specified. Stops the clock of the current active task if it has been started.

using
  Reports the name of the current active task


The Clock
=======================

start
  Starts the clock for the active task

stop
  Stops the clock for the active task


Reporting
=======================

status
  Reports the current time elapsed for the active task

report
  Reports hours for all tasks


Other
=======================

exit
  Quits the program
